316
00:15:04,333 --> 00:15:06,013
<i>You'll have a great time
with him and Emmy.</i>

317
00:15:06,041 --> 00:15:07,291
Eh, have you met them?

318
00:15:07,791 --> 00:15:11,625
They're very... upbeat.
