What the hell am I doing here?

327
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:35,208
[Damien] <i>You're protecting your career</i>

328
00:15:35,291 --> 00:15:36,416
<i>and the paper.</i>

329
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:38,000
<i>We need to be careful.</i>

330
00:15:38,083 --> 00:15:41,791
