to leave West Cork.

376
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,833
- We love it here.
- Well, what's not to love?

377
00:17:53,916 --> 00:17:54,750
[chuckles]

378
00:17:54,833 --> 00:17:56,333
So, this podcast,

379
00:17:56,416 --> 00:17:59,291
are you doing that thing
where you say it's about one thing,

